---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Sidebar from '../../components/Sidebar.astro';
const title = "Age--metallicity relations (AMRs)";
import WikiLink from '../../components/WikiLink.astro';
---
<Base title={title}>
  <Sidebar />
  <main class="page-main">
    <h1 class="page-title">Age--metallicity relations</h1>
    <p>Age--metallicity relations (AMRs) trace how the metallicity of a stellar population increases with time within a system; they are used to infer chemical evolution histories of galaxies and progenitors.</p>
    <h2>Applications</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Reconstructing progenitor chemical evolution from globular cluster populations (see <WikiLink slug="pages/lardo_2026_gc_progenitors" text="Lardo et al. 2026" />).</li>
    </ul>
  </main>
</Base>
